div.note:
I saw  . . . and corporally:  This long passage on Rev 13:1-2 is all
    but lifted from de Coninck's rendering of Bale (Bilde, Cc3v-Dd2;
    Image, 214-8).

I
	  saw (sayth . . . or whatsoeuer: Cf. Bale (Image, 286;
	  Bilde, Qq5v).

and shed very . . . any more: See Bale (Image, 309-17;
    Bilde, Tt7v-Xx2r). Van der Noot imitates Bale freely here, sometimes
    expanding and sometimes condensing.
